    <p>To com­mem­o­rate World Phys­i­cal Ther­apy Day this year, Tan Tock Seng Hospi­tal is con­duct­ing a Face­book Live talk show ti­tled Care­giv­ing Starts from The In­side Out, fo­cus­ing on care­givers’ phys­i­cal and men­tal well-be­ing. The panel of ex­perts com­prises a geri­atric doc­tor, psy­chol­o­gist and phys­io­ther­a­pist. They will dis­cuss how to rein in stress and re­gain a sense of bal­ance and joy while car­ing for your loved ones.</p>
    <p>Sept 5, 9 - 10.30am</p>
    <p>Free with reg­is­tra­tion face­book.com/ TanTock­SengHospi­tal</p>


